Dale Evans https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dale_Evans 0 Dale Evans Rogers (born Lucille Wood Smith; October 31, 1912 – February 7, 2001) was an American actress, singer, and songwriter. She was the third wife of singing cowboy Roy Rogers. Dale_Evans_Rogers ( born Lucille_Wood_Smith ; October_31_,_1912 – February_7_,_2001 ) was an_American_actress , singer , and songwriter .
